{"tid":2413980,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾志偉臨陣煞停《聲夢傳奇》死敵余詠珊承認獲通知活動延期","createTime":"2021-02-19T05:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T10:36:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ee60b419a52344fd3a8836d56bc9736535adb0cb","tid":2413980,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:49:23.000Z","msg":"余詠珊未削權前，除了負責大台網上平台外，當日眼見ViuTV搞的《全民造星III》有聲有色，於是她與老公何哲圖「一手策劃」《聲夢傳奇》對撼，安排15位參賽者接受唱歌及舞台訓練，為TVB星夢娛樂打造新星。<br />\n<br />\n余詠珊被全面削權，除了將大權拱手相讓外，《聲夢》亦隨時被腰斬，淪為倉底貨。今日有周刊報道指這個比賽節目原定在下月7日周日晚播出，不過已經被煞停了，無綫決定由原先在周六晚播出的《流行經典50年》頂上，而周六晚則改播《尹光鬼馬笑不停演唱會》，余詠珊回覆傳媒時承認收到《聲夢》延期的通知，所有事情等志偉安排和決定，已經與她無關，她亦透露除了《聲夢》外，晚上10時半的節目、big big shop和big big channel也會under志偉。節目監製陳旭亮接受傳媒訪問時承認節目「Hold住」，一切待曾志偉決定，與此同時，有指志偉找來何麗全回歸，近日他已經與四大唱片公司會面，暫時情況相當樂觀。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210219/JWLISLNBHBCCXC2LYRAACAWPXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210219%2FJWLISLNBHBCCXC2LYRAACAWPXA%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69EcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=fb70d692\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210219%2FJWLISLNBHBCCXC2LYRAACAWPXA%2F&h=16ca32f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210219/JWLISLNBHBCCXC2LYRAACAWPXA/</a>"},{"pid":"1502b405962b037d99394648e210961a434ea4f2","tid":2413980,"uid":44854,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"無人睇咪腰斬<br />\n好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829be7b3cfed854049520c76e0477491357d2127","tid":2413980,"uid":300782,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"尹光正呀"},{"pid":"d387e2feae1ebd0d3b942751bfc764464535373a","tid":2413980,"uid":269864,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"ee60b419a52344fd3a8836d56bc9736535adb0cb","tid":2413980,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"